{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, he beat the living daylight out of this guy, and he walked away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- and we shared-- this group always, whoever found something, or was able to get a hold of something, we all shared.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were seven of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Three brothers, my present brother-in-law-- which he married my sister after the war, and my cousin, who we went from one camp to another, Jack Rosenbaum so-- and a few other people-- one other person, actually, and three-- and the three brothers who were butchers so they were hunky guys, and-- and that's why we always-- we always stayed together and helped each other.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You said that you had lost Jack in the ghetto in Sosnowitz, I think, or--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but then we were reunited again in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were reunited in Auschwitz, and we-- from Auschwitz we went to Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were together on a death march, and-- and-- we must have lost maybe close to half the people that we started out of from Funfteichen to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Gross-Rosen, we were taken into barracks that didn't have any baths.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- there was no room because they-- they collected all these people to Gross-Rosen, the collector's camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were-- we was sitting like a herring.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had to sit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- you spread-- you had to spread your legs, and the next guy would sit in front of you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were sitting behind you, and if you had to go to the bathroom, the whole row would have to stand up because there was no room-- there were like wall-to-wall people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the-- and there were terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot of people got sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was diseases.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
